%h1 Images
%p By default, images are set to be responsive.
%p Illustrations and images both allow for setting tooltips

%h3 Standard image using the :image option
.row
  .col-lg-3.col
    %p
      %b Tooltips are available:
      = ui.nfg :image, image: 'test_app/sample_illustration.png', tooltip: 'With a tooltip'

%hr

%h3 Standard image with responsive set to false
= ui.nfg :image, image: 'test_app/sample_illustration.png', responsive: false


%h3 Standard image using the :src option
.row
  .col-lg-4.col
    = ui.nfg :image, src: 'test_app/sample_illustration.png'

%hr

%h3 An image with no image or src
= ui.nfg :image